INSERT ArticleRevisions (ArticleId, [Text], RevisionReason, CreatedByAspNetUserId)
VALUES (SCOPE_IDENTITY(), N'*FRUiTS* 杂志是一本日本街头时尚杂志，由摄影师田崎敬一（Aoki Shoichi）于1997年创立，其工作室位于东京涉谷区。该杂志专注于记录和展示日本街头时尚，特别是那些受到哈拉杰库文化影响的人。2017年，田崎宣布该杂志将不再出版，原因是在他看来，哈拉杰库的街头时尚已不再具有独特性。' + CHAR(13) + CHAR(10) + CHAR(13) + CHAR(10) + N'## 内容与特色' + CHAR(13) + CHAR(10) + CHAR(13) + CHAR(10) + N'*FRUiTS* 杂志以其对街头时尚的深度报道而闻名，尤其是那些独特且个性化的装扮。每一期都包含了大量的街拍照片，这些照片不仅展示了个人的时尚品味，也反映了日本哈拉杰库区独特的时尚潮流。' + CHAR(13) + CHAR(10) + CHAR(13) + CHAR(10) + N'在它的二十年出版历史中，*FRUiTS* 成功地记录了哈拉杰库的时尚演变，从最初的“娃娃风”到“哥特萝莉”，再到“装饰性少女”，每一种风格都在这个杂志的页面上找到了展现的空间。这些深入报道和真实的街头照片，使 *FRUiTS* 成为理解和欣赏日本街头时尚的重要窗口。' + CHAR(13) + CHAR(10) + CHAR(13) + CHAR(10) + N'## 影响和遗产' + CHAR(13) + CHAR(10) + CHAR(13) + CHAR(10) + N'*FRUiTS* 杂志在全球范围内对街头时尚的影响力不容小觑。杂志通过对哈拉杰库独特风格的长期报道，将其推向了全球的视野。许多西方的设计师和时尚爱好者，都从这本杂志中获得了灵感和启发。' + CHAR(13) + CHAR(10) + CHAR(13) + CHAR(10) + N'虽然 *FRUiTS* 在2017年停止出版，但它在时尚界的影响仍在持续。这本杂志为时尚研究者和爱好者提供了一个宝贵的资源，帮助他们了解和研究日本街头时尚的演变和影响力。' + CHAR(13) + CHAR(10) + CHAR(13) + CHAR(10) + N'总的来说，*FRUiTS* 杂志是对日本哈拉杰库街头时尚最深入、最真实的记录，它的出版历史本身就是哈拉杰库时尚演变的缩影。', N'Article created.', '7240be61-df81-46f9-8152-6a48b96abc40');

INSERT Articles (Title, UrlSlug, SiteId, Culture)
VALUES ( N'Men''s Non-no', N'mens-non-no', 1, 'en' );
INSERT ArticleRevisions (ArticleId, [Text], RevisionReason, CreatedByAspNetUserId)
VALUES (SCOPE_IDENTITY(), N'*Men''s Non-no* is a leading men''s fashion and lifestyle magazine based in Japan. It was first published in 1986 as a counterpart to the women''s fashion magazine *Non-no*, both of which are produced by the Shueisha publishing company.' + CHAR(13) + CHAR(10) + CHAR(13) + CHAR(10) + N'The creation of *Men''s Non-no* was influenced by the changing dynamics of men''s fashion in the 1980s, as a growing number of men began to take a keen interest in personal style. Recognizing this trend, Shueisha launched *Men''s Non-no* to cater to the burgeoning demand for men''s fashion content.' + CHAR(13) + CHAR(10) + CHAR(13) + CHAR(10) + N'## Content and Features' + CHAR(13) + CHAR(10) + CHAR(13) + CHAR(10) + N'*Men''s Non-no* provides a comprehensive range of content focused on men''s fashion, lifestyle, and culture. It covers a diverse array of styles from high-end designer brands to streetwear labels, showcasing the latest trends and providing style advice to its readers.' + CHAR(13) + CHAR(10) + CHAR(13) + CHAR(10) + N'A defining feature of the magazine is its highly visual content, featuring fashion spreads and editorials that combine vibrant photography with distinctive layout designs. The magazine frequently collaborates with renowned photographers and stylists to create visually compelling content that reflects the contemporary fashion landscape.' + CHAR(13) + CHAR(10) + CHAR(13) + CHAR(10) + N'In addition to fashion, *Men''s Non-no* covers topics such as grooming, health and fitness, travel, music, film, and technology, offering a well-rounded perspective on modern men''s lifestyle.' + CHAR(13) + CHAR(10) + CHAR(13) + CHAR(10) + N'The magazine also features interviews with prominent figures from various industries, including fashion designers, musicians, actors, and athletes, providing readers with unique insights into their lives and careers.' + CHAR(13) + CHAR(10) + CHAR(13) + CHAR(10) + N'## Influence and Legacy' + CHAR(13) + CHAR(10) + CHAR(13) + CHAR(10) + N'*Men''s Non-no* has exerted a significant influence on the men''s fashion industry in Japan and beyond. It has been instrumental in popularizing various fashion trends, and its pages have served as a launchpad for numerous models and actors who have gone on to achieve fame in Japan and overseas.' + CHAR(13) + CHAR(10) + CHAR(13) + CHAR(10) + N'Over the years, the magazine has consistently stayed ahead of fashion trends, and its commitment to high-quality content and innovative visual storytelling has solidified its status as a must-read publication for fashion-conscious men.' + CHAR(13) + CHAR(10) + CHAR(13) + CHAR(10) + N'Through its thoughtful coverage of fashion and lifestyle, *Men''s Non-no* has played a crucial role in shaping the conversation around men''s style and culture, contributing to the broader cultural shift towards the acceptance and celebration of men''s interest in fashion. Its enduring popularity testifies to its ability to evolve with the times while staying true to its core mission of providing readers with the latest in men''s fashion and lifestyle.', N'Article created.', '7240be61-df81-46f9-8152-6a48b96abc40');

INSERT Articles (Title, UrlSlug, SiteId, Culture)
VALUES ( N'Zigzag', N'zigzag', 1, 'en' );
INSERT ArticleRevisions (ArticleId, [Text], RevisionReason, CreatedByAspNetUserId)
VALUES (SCOPE_IDENTITY(), N'*Zigzag* is an esteemed surfing magazine based in South Africa. Established in 1976 by Paul Botha, a notable figure in the South African surfing scene, the magazine has been an instrumental platform for promoting surfing in South Africa and abroad. Botha''s passion for the sport, coupled with his journalistic acumen, ensured *Zigzag*''s rapid ascent as a beloved publication amongst the surfing community.' + CHAR(13) + CHAR(10) + CHAR(13) + CHAR(10) + N'## Content and Features' + CHAR(13) + CHAR(10) + CHAR(13) + CHAR(10) + N'The magazine is famed for its coverage of all things surfing, encompassing news, features, interviews, and stunning photography. The publication provides a platform for both established and up-and-coming surfers, showcasing their talent and stories to a wider audience. ' + CHAR(13) + CHAR(10) + CHAR(13) + CHAR(10) + N'One of *Zigzag*''s distinguishing features is its stunning and vivid photography. Capturing the thrill and beauty of the sport, the magazine''s visuals transport readers to the heart of the action, whether it be a local beach break or an exotic international location. ' + CHAR(13) + CHAR(10) + CHAR(13) + CHAR(10) + N'In addition to its focus on surfing, *Zigzag* also delves into environmental issues impacting the oceans and coastlines. The magazine takes its role as a custodian of the sport seriously, fostering dialogues about environmental stewardship and sustainability within the surfing community.' + CHAR(13) + CHAR(10) + CHAR(13) + CHAR(10) + N'## Influence and Legacy' + CHAR(13) + CHAR(10) + CHAR(13) + CHAR(10) + N'Over the years, *Zigzag* has earned its reputation as a leading authority in the world of surfing. The magazine has been instrumental in documenting the evolution of the sport in South Africa, from its nascent beginnings to its current status as a globally recognized and respected discipline. ' + CHAR(13) + CHAR(10) + CHAR(13) + CHAR(10) + N'As the longest-running surfing magazine in Africa, *Zigzag* has played a crucial role in championing the continent''s surfing scene. It has highlighted the talents of African surfers, showcased the continent''s world-class surfing locations, and brought international attention to the region''s unique surfing culture.' + CHAR(13) + CHAR(10) + CHAR(13) + CHAR(10) + N'Throughout its history, *Zigzag* has evolved in response to the changing needs of its readership and the surfing community. In 2012, the magazine adopted a digital-first strategy, focusing on its online platform while still producing print editions. This shift allowed *Zigzag* to reach a wider, global audience and further cemented its place as an innovative leader in surf journalism. ' + CHAR(13) + CHAR(10) + CHAR(13) + CHAR(10) + N'While *Zigzag* is deeply rooted in South African surf culture, its influence and readership extend well beyond its home shores. It continues to inspire, inform, and engage readers with its exceptional coverage of the sport, reinforcing its position as a seminal voice in global surf culture.', N'Article created.', '7240be61-df81-46f9-8152-6a48b96abc40');

INSERT Articles (Title, UrlSlug, SiteId, Culture)
VALUES ( N'Luxury Pools', N'luxury-pools', 1, 'en' );
INSERT ArticleRevisions (ArticleId, [Text], RevisionReason, CreatedByAspNetUserId)
VALUES (SCOPE_IDENTITY(), N'*Luxury Pools* magazine is a premium biannual publication that has set the standard for showcasing the world''s most extraordinary swimming pools and outdoor living spaces since its inception in 1997. It was founded by RMS Media Group, a company based in Massachusetts, USA, with a vision to provide a dedicated platform to celebrate, explore, and inspire high-end pool design and outdoor living.' + CHAR(13) + CHAR(10) + CHAR(13) + CHAR(10) + N'## Content and Features' + CHAR(13) + CHAR(10) + CHAR(13) + CHAR(10) + N'Each issue of *Luxury Pools* presents an immersive exploration of the world''s most impressive pools and outdoor spaces. The magazine is characterized by its meticulously curated high-resolution photographs, detailed architectural plans, and engaging articles that delve into the design process, materials used, and the unique features of each project.' + CHAR(13) + CHAR(10) + CHAR(13) + CHAR(10) + N'While the focus is primarily on luxury pools, the magazine also covers all elements of upscale outdoor living spaces. This includes innovative landscaping design, custom spas, water features, outdoor kitchens, and poolside architecture. *Luxury Pools* showcases the work of world-renowned designers, architects, and landscape artists, making it a leading source of inspiration for those interested in luxury outdoor living.' + CHAR(13) + CHAR(10) + CHAR(13) + CHAR(10) + N'One of the magazine’s standout features is its in-depth designer and builder profiles. These pieces offer readers an inside look at the creative minds behind the stunning designs, providing insight into their creative processes, design philosophies, and their perspectives on upcoming trends in the industry.' + CHAR(13) + CHAR(10) + CHAR(13) + CHAR(10) + N'## Influence and Legacy' + CHAR(13) + CHAR(10) + CHAR(13) + CHAR(10) + N'*Luxury Pools* has carved out a unique niche for itself within the home design publishing industry. By focusing exclusively on high-end pool and outdoor living design, the magazine offers a unique perspective not found in general home design publications.' + CHAR(13) + CHAR(10) + CHAR(13) + CHAR(10) + N'As a leading authority in its field, *Luxury Pools* has had a profound impact on the outdoor living design industry. The publication has been instrumental in promoting innovative design, advanced pool technology, and superior craftsmanship. Its influence can be seen in the increasing sophistication and creativity of luxury pool design around the world.' + CHAR(13) + CHAR(10) + CHAR(13) + CHAR(10) + N'The magazine''s ongoing success attests to its appeal among its target audience of affluent homeowners, architects, and designers. While the publication caters to a luxury market, its reach extends to anyone seeking inspiration and insight into the possibilities of pool design and outdoor living. *Luxury Pools* continues to inspire and influence the world of luxury outdoor design.', N'Article created.', '7240be61-df81-46f9-8152-6a48b96abc40');

INSERT Articles (Title, UrlSlug, SiteId, Culture)
VALUES ( N'Non-no', N'non-no', 1, 'en' );
INSERT ArticleRevisions (ArticleId, [Text], RevisionReason, CreatedByAspNetUserId)
VALUES (SCOPE_IDENTITY(), N'*Non-no* (ノン－ノ) is a Japanese women''s fashion and lifestyle magazine published by Shueisha. The magazine''s headquarters are located in Tokyo, Japan. Established in 1971, *Non-no* was initially a fortnightly publication, with the first issue appearing in February of that year. The magazine has a longer history compared to other Japanese fashion magazines such as Cawaii!, Olive, and the like. It targets teens and young women in their early 20s. ' + CHAR(13) + CHAR(10) + CHAR(13) + CHAR(10) + N'Unlike other magazines that focus on gossip, *Non-no*, along with another women''s magazine, An An, provides its readers with materials aimed at developing their self-identity. The magazine had a circulation of 850,000 copies in 1978, which decreased to 440,870 copies by the year 2006.' + CHAR(13) + CHAR(10) + CHAR(13) + CHAR(10) + N'In addition to the women''s version, a male demographic targeted counterpart, *Men''s Non-no*, was launched by Shueisha on 25 May 1987.' + CHAR(13) + CHAR(10) + CHAR(13) + CHAR(10) + N'Over the years, *Non-no* has featured numerous models. The current models as of 2023 include Yūka Suzuki (2014–present), Fumika Baba (2015–present), Nanaka Matsukawa (2017–present), Risa Watanabe (2017–present), Manami Enosawa (2018–present), Asuka Kijima (2018–present), Mirei Sasaki (2019-present), Sakura Endo (2020-present), Mayu Yokota (2020-present), Ayaka Konno (2021-present), and Kanon (2022-present).' + CHAR(13) + CHAR(10) + CHAR(13) + CHAR(10) + N'The magazine also features a rich history of past models. This includes names such as Airi Tanaka, Akiko Kikuchi, Anne Watanabe, Ayumi, Azusa Takehana, Emi, Etsuko Sugai, Hana, Hana Matsushima, Izumi Yamaguchi, Keiko Kurihara, Lina Ohta, Manami Teruya, Michi Ōmori, Miki, Momoko Nagano, Nishida Naomi, Noriko Amakasu, Satsuki Katayama, Shiho, Yasue Sato, Yuko Gomiyo, Sachie Futamura, Mina Sayado, Yasuko Matsuyuki (1990s), Yui Natsukawa (1990s), Ryō (1990s), Sachiko Katō (1990s), Koyuki (1990s), Kimiko Mori (1999–2001), Miho Tanaka (2000–2012), Ema Fujisawa (2001–2005), Sachiko Ogata (2002–2005), Rena Takeshita (2004–2009), Miyu Kogawa (2004–2010), Momoko Kuroki (2005–2007), Mew Azama (2006–2007), Miyu (2006–2010), Saori Watanabe (2007–2010), Emi Takahashi (2007–2011), Mikiko Yano (2008–2012), Cecil Kishimoto (2008–2015), and Yumi Yamamoto (2009–2010).' + CHAR(13) + CHAR(10) + CHAR(13) + CHAR(10) + N'Overall, *Non-no* represents an influential publication in Japan''s fashion and lifestyle scene, contributing not only to fashion trends but also to personal development and identity among its readers.{{Categories Magazines}}', N'Article created.', '7240be61-df81-46f9-8152-6a48b96abc40');

INSERT Articles ( Title, UrlSlug, [Text], RevisionReason, CreatedByAspNetUserId, SiteId, Language ) VALUES ( N'Haya', N'haya', N'Haya (Arabic: هيا) is a prominent Arabic-language magazine catering to glamorous, fashion-savvy, and fun-loving women in the Middle East. It is targeted at a demographic between the ages of 21 and 45, aiming to provide engaging and relevant content to its readership.' + CHAR(13) + CHAR(10) + CHAR(13) + CHAR(10) + 'The magazine covers a wide range of topics, including fashion, beauty, lifestyle, entertainment, relationships, health, and more. Haya seeks to inspire and empower its readers by showcasing the latest fashion trends, offering style advice, and featuring profiles of influential women.' + CHAR(13) + CHAR(10) + CHAR(13) + CHAR(10) + 'Fashion is a key focus of Haya magazine. It presents readers with stylish looks, runway trends, and fashion editorials, allowing them to stay up-to-date with the ever-changing fashion landscape. The magazine often features renowned designers, emerging talents, and local fashion brands, highlighting the diversity and creativity of the fashion industry in the Middle East.' + CHAR(13) + CHAR(10) + CHAR(13) + CHAR(10) + 'In addition to fashion, Haya covers beauty and skincare extensively. It provides readers with beauty tips, product recommendations, and tutorials to help them enhance their beauty routines. The magazine features makeup artists, hairstylists, and beauty experts, offering insights into the latest beauty trends and techniques.' + CHAR(13) + CHAR(10) + CHAR(13) + CHAR(10) + 'Haya also delves into various lifestyle subjects. It covers travel destinations, home decor, food and recipes, wellness, and fitness. The magazine aims to provide a well-rounded view of the modern woman''s lifestyle, offering content that is informative, entertaining, and relevant to its readers'' interests and aspirations.' + CHAR(13) + CHAR(10) + CHAR(13) + CHAR(10) + 'Entertainment is another significant aspect of Haya magazine. It features interviews with celebrities, profiles of influential individuals, and coverage of cultural events, concerts, and film premieres. The magazine offers glimpses into the lives of public figures, providing readers with an insider perspective on the region''s entertainment industry.' + CHAR(13) + CHAR(10) + CHAR(13) + CHAR(10) + 'Haya prides itself on its visually appealing layout and high-quality photography. The magazine uses vibrant imagery and creative visuals to captivate readers and create an immersive reading experience.' + CHAR(13) + CHAR(10) + CHAR(13) + CHAR(10) + 'As the leading Arabic-language magazine in the Middle East, Haya has established itself as a trusted source of fashion, beauty, and lifestyle content. It aims to celebrate the glamour, individuality, and diversity of women in the region while providing them with the tools and inspiration to lead stylish and fulfilling lives.' + CHAR(13) + CHAR(10) + CHAR(13) + CHAR(10) + 'Overall, Haya magazine caters to a wide range of interests for fashion-forward women in the Middle East. It combines the latest trends, expert advice, and captivating content to engage and inspire its readership, reflecting the vibrant and dynamic nature of the region''s fashion and lifestyle scene.', N'Article created', '7240be61-df81-46f9-8152-6a48b96abc40', 1, 'en' );
INSERT Articles ( Title, UrlSlug, [Text], RevisionReason, CreatedByAspNetUserId, SiteId, Language ) VALUES ( N'Popeye', N'popeye', N'Popeye is a renowned Japanese monthly men''s fashion and lifestyle magazine based in Tokyo. It is widely regarded as one of the oldest and most influential publications focusing on men''s fashion in Japan. The magazine''s tagline, "Magazine for City Boys," reflects its emphasis on urban style and lifestyle.' + CHAR(13) + CHAR(10) + CHAR(13) + CHAR(10) + 'Popeye was founded in 1976 by Yasuo Tanaka, who also served as the editor-in-chief. From its inception, the magazine aimed to provide men with a fresh perspective on fashion, grooming, and urban culture. It quickly gained popularity and became a leading voice in the Japanese fashion industry.' + CHAR(13) + CHAR(10) + CHAR(13) + CHAR(10) + 'Popeye''s content revolves around men''s fashion, covering a wide range of topics including clothing, footwear, accessories, and grooming. The magazine showcases the latest fashion trends, offers style advice, and features interviews with designers and industry insiders. It caters to the interests of fashion-conscious men who appreciate both classic and cutting-edge styles.' + CHAR(13) + CHAR(10) + CHAR(13) + CHAR(10) + 'Beyond fashion, Popeye explores various aspects of men''s lifestyle. It covers topics such as art, music, technology, travel, food, and popular culture. The magazine aims to provide a holistic view of the modern urban man''s interests and aspirations.' + CHAR(13) + CHAR(10) + CHAR(13) + CHAR(10) + 'Popeye has been recognized for its high-quality editorial content and visually striking layout. It features engaging photography, captivating artwork, and innovative design elements that enhance the reading experience.' + CHAR(13) + CHAR(10) + CHAR(13) + CHAR(10) + 'Throughout its history, Popeye has remained at the forefront of men''s fashion in Japan, consistently featuring influential designers, brands, and cultural icons. The magazine has played a significant role in shaping men''s fashion trends and inspiring readers to embrace their individual style.' + CHAR(13) + CHAR(10) + CHAR(13) + CHAR(10) + 'As one of the oldest men''s fashion magazines in Japan, Popeye has established a loyal readership and continues to be highly regarded within the industry. Its insightful content, unique perspective, and focus on urban lifestyle have contributed to its enduring popularity.' + CHAR(13) + CHAR(10) + CHAR(13) + CHAR(10) + 'Overall, Popeye magazine represents a comprehensive resource for men seeking inspiration, guidance, and a deeper understanding of fashion and lifestyle trends. It has contributed significantly to the development and evolution of men''s fashion in Japan and has maintained its relevance by staying true to its mission of being a go-to publication for city-dwelling men.', N'Article created', '7240be61-df81-46f9-8152-6a48b96abc40', 1, 'en' );
INSERT Articles ( Title, UrlSlug, [Text], RevisionReason, CreatedByAspNetUserId, SiteId, Language ) VALUES ( N'Seventeen (Japan)', N'seventeen-japan', N'Seventeen (セブンティーン, Sebuntīn) is a popular monthly Japanese fashion magazine aimed at teenage girls. Published by Shueisha, it has a long history and has evolved over the years to cater to the changing interests and needs of its readers.' + CHAR(13) + CHAR(10) + CHAR(13) + CHAR(10) + 'The magazine was first launched in Japan in 1967 as a weekly publication, taking inspiration from the original American Seventeen magazine. The Japanese edition sought to provide fashion and lifestyle content specifically tailored to the interests and tastes of teenage girls in Japan.' + CHAR(13) + CHAR(10) + CHAR(13) + CHAR(10) + 'Initially, the magazine operated as a weekly publication, but in 1987 it transitioned into a monthly format. This change allowed for more in-depth coverage and a broader range of content. The name was also officially changed to "SEVENTEEN" to match the American edition. In 2008, the magazine underwent another name change and is now simply known as "Seventeen."' + CHAR(13) + CHAR(10) + CHAR(13) + CHAR(10) + 'Seventeen magazine covers a wide array of topics, primarily focusing on fashion, beauty, lifestyle, and entertainment. It showcases the latest fashion trends, provides style advice, and offers tips for hair, makeup, and skincare. The magazine features fashion spreads, highlighting both local and international brands, and provides readers with practical styling tips and shopping suggestions.' + CHAR(13) + CHAR(10) + CHAR(13) + CHAR(10) + 'In addition to fashion and beauty, Seventeen delves into various aspects of teenage girls'' lives. It covers topics such as relationships, school, health, self-improvement, and personal development. The magazine often features interviews with celebrities, profiles of inspiring individuals, and real-life stories that resonate with its readership.' + CHAR(13) + CHAR(10) + C